he bytecode and each opcode is encoded as one byte, except for PUSH opcodes."), mdx("p", null, "Solidity is a high-level programming language that we understand, but machines do not. When we run an Ethereum client such as Geth Classic, Geth, Multi-Geth, or Parity Ethereum, it also comes with the operating system (the EVM) specifically created to run smart contracts."), mdx("p", null, "Soon EVM-LLVM will be ready for alpha tests. Feel free to visit the official EVM-LLVM project repo here ", "[4]", " for the latest developments. If you would like to collaborate on this project don\u2019t be shy to start contributed or ping Alan Li, our Lead Compiler Engineer, on ETC Labs Discord ", "[5]", "."), mdx("p", null, "Resources:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
